'''国际正义联盟'''（{{lang-en|Justice League International}}，简称为'''JLI'''）是一支[[DC漫画|DC漫画]][[超级英雄|超级英雄]]战队，由作者{{le|凱思·吉芬|Keith Giffen}}和{{le|J. M. 迪麥提斯|J. M. DeMatteis}}和画家{{le|凯文·马奎尔 (画家)|Kevin Maguire (artist)|凯文·马奎尔}}于1987年创作<ref>{{cite book|last=Manning|first= Matthew K.|last2=Dolan|first2=Hannah, ed.|chapter= 1980s|title = DC Comics Year By Year A Visual Chronicle|publisher=[[Dorling_Kindersley|Dorling Kindersley]] |year=2010 |isbn= 978-0-7566-6742-9 |page= 228 |quote = It was clear that the [Justice League] needed a major overhaul. But no one quite expected how drastic the transformation would truly be in the hands of writers Keith Giffen and J. M. DeMatteis and artist Kevin Maguire.}}</ref>。

